task.summary:
Lab 2
Added functionality for loading locally saved data if a user is logged in and displaying info on preferences profile layout.

Lab 2
Added functionality for locally saving settings. No actual effect on phone yet.

Lab 2
Made availability check before saving. onSaveClick checks availability, if character name is available, doSave is called, otherwise tell user to enter a new one.
Requested permissions from user, handled permissions accordingly.
Fixed bug with password popup when clicking outside of box.
Removed Sign In button click intent. Only way to access an account is to create it.
Added Toasts in various places to keep user informed on ongoing processes.
